parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Apptainer",
  "software": [
    "Apptainer 1.1.9",
    "OpenMPI",
    "Intel MPI",
    "MPICH-CH4",
    "MPICH-CH4b",
    "MPICH-CH3",
    "PMIX",
    "PMI2"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    "2 nodes",
    "2 tasks per node",
    "exclusive access to nodes",
    "2 hours runtime",
    "0 MB memory"
  ],
  "environment_variables": [
    "STARTDIR",
    "CDIR",
    "SLURM_JOB_ID",
    "OMP_NUM_THREADS",
    "MPI",
    "PMIX_MCA_gds"
  ],
  "files": [
    "alpine.sif",
    "openmpi.sif",
    "intel.sif",
    "mpich_ch4.sif",
    "mpich_ch4b.sif",
    "mpich_ch3.sif",
    "/opt/examples/affinity/tds/phostone",
    "/opt/examples/affinity/tds/ppong",
    "tymer",
    "warnings",
    "output",
    "script",
    "env"
  ],
  "commands": [
    "module load apptainer",
    "which apptainer",
    "hostname",
    "apptainer exec $CDIR/alpine.sif hostname",
    "srun -n 1 --nodes=1 apptainer exec $CDIR/alpine.sif cat /etc/os-release",
    "srun  --mpi=$MPI   apptainer  exec   $CDIR/$v.sif  /opt/examples/affinity/tds/phostone -F",
    "srun  --mpi=$MPI   apptainer  exec   $CDIR/$v.sif  /opt/examples/affinity/tds/ppong"
  ]
}
```
